{"tid":1522873,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"愛護狗隻 刻不容緩","createTime":"2019-08-31T14:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T14:49:08.000Z","uid":300946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"16a53b6bffa2a9eb23c4f67224e98ff7153d7b84","tid":1522873,"uid":300946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:47:41.000Z","msg":"既然全香港人都咁鐘意黑狗<br />\n所有人都應該要係自己崗位愛護佢哋<br />\n<br />\n飲食嘅手足一早就開始加料俾黑狗 <br />\n等佢哋OT咁辛苦可以食得好啲<br />\n咁其他行業嘅你哋呢？<br />\n加價去提供更優質服務？<br />\n預留最佳嘅時段為佢哋服務？<br />\n<br />\n記得要愛屋及烏，愛護埋佢哋冚家，我就玩開3P賞賜佢哋老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛護狗隻 刻不容緩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KGS2JbQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKGS2JbQ.jpg&h=c2a35805&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed798a51b11998fe5be3fc87d6149124390b6502","tid":1522873,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:49:08.000Z","msg":"改口叫老鼠"}]}